'''Fry Industries''' was a security systems manufacturing corporation founded by [[Talesan Fry]] just outside the city of [[Bruit]] on [[Genian]]. They developed and manufactured surveillance, communications, and security systems during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

